# Development-only files that should not ship in the published plugin zip.
# `git archive` (the basis of the Moodle plugin release zip) honours
# export-ignore. Plugin code, language strings, templates, AMD build output and
# the PHPUnit/Behat tests are all kept — only CI/repo tooling is stripped.
/.github        export-ignore
/.gitignore     export-ignore
/.gitattributes export-ignore
